{"type":"message","id":"631d2867","parentId":"c7fd6fbe","timestamp":"2026-03-20T04:53:41.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到！这是明天外出拍摄的通知：\n\n**明天（3月21日）安排提醒：**\n- ⏰ **集合时间**：8:20\n- 📍 **集合地点**：青少年宫\n- 🚌 **交通**：统一乘车\n\n**需要准备的物品：**\n- ✅ 水杯\n- ✅ 毛巾\n- ✅ 小外套\n\n**注意事项：**\n- 🍽️ 吃好早餐再上车\n- 🚫 不要带零食或食品\n\n主人需要我设置一个明天早上的提醒吗？比如 7:30 提醒准备物品，8:00 提醒出发？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773982415162}}
