{"type":"message","id":"68252407","parentId":"d73c9942","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:31:11.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"目前还没有配置每日反思的定时任务。让我为你创建一个："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.cron:56","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"每日工作反思","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 2 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行每日自我反思任务：\n\n1. 查看过去24小时内的会话记录（使用 sessions_list --activeMinutes 1440）\n2. 分析每个会话：\n   - 什么做得好？（任务顺利完成、高效工具使用等）\n   - 什么出了问题？（错误、重试、误解等）\n   - 学到了什么？（具体、可操作的教训）\n3. 将反思结果写入适当的文件：\n   - 流程改进 → AGENTS.md\n   - 工具使用技巧 → TOOLS.md  \n   - 今日事件 → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n   - 用户偏好 → memory/about-user.md\n4. 生成简短总结（2-4句话）\n\n注意：\n- 只提取真正的教训，不要简单总结\n- 检查是否已有类似记录，避免重复\n- 保持简洁具体，不要泛泛而谈"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu"}}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774013461461}}
{"type":"message","id":"2dbaf036","parentId":"68252407","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:31:11.811Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.cron:56","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"d0aff8be-c82f-4fc5-aa1f-8e3a20f50a03\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n  \"name\": \"每日工作反思\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1774013471787,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1774013471787,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 2 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"请执行每日自我反思任务：\\n\\n1. 查看过去24小时内的会话记录（使用 sessions_list --activeMinutes 1440）\\n2. 分析每个会话：\\n   - 什么做得好？（任务顺利完成、高效工具使用等）\\n   - 什么出了问题？（错误、重试、误解等）\\n   - 学到了什么？（具体、可操作的教训）\\n3. 将反思结果写入适当的文件：\\n   - 流程改进 → AGENTS.md\\n   - 工具使用技巧 → TOOLS.md  \\n   - 今日事件 → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\\n   - 用户偏好 → memory/about-user.md\\n4. 生成简短总结（2-4句话）\\n\\n注意：\\n- 只提取真正的教训，不要简单总结\\n- 检查是否已有类似记录，避免重复\\n- 保持简洁具体，不要泛泛而谈\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774029600000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"d0aff8be-c82f-4fc5-aa1f-8e3a20f50a03","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"每日工作反思","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774013471787,"updatedAtMs":1774013471787,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 2 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行每日自我反思任务：\n\n1. 查看过去24小时内的会话记录（使用 sessions_list --activeMinutes 1440）\n2. 分析每个会话：\n   - 什么做得好？（任务顺利完成、高效工具使用等）\n   - 什么出了问题？（错误、重试、误解等）\n   - 学到了什么？（具体、可操作的教训）\n3. 将反思结果写入适当的文件：\n   - 流程改进 → AGENTS.md\n   - 工具使用技巧 → TOOLS.md  \n   - 今日事件 → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n   - 用户偏好 → memory/about-user.md\n4. 生成简短总结（2-4句话）\n\n注意：\n- 只提取真正的教训，不要简单总结\n- 检查是否已有类似记录，避免重复\n- 保持简洁具体，不要泛泛而谈"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774029600000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774013471799}}
{"type":"message","id":"50b79ab3","parentId":"2dbaf036","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:31:37.006Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完成！✅ 我已经配置了**每日凌晨2点的自动反思任务**。\n\n**反思任务详情：**\n- ⏰ **时间**：每天凌晨 2:00\n- 📊 **内容**：分析过去24小时的工作对话\n- 📝 **输出**：\n  - 成功经验 → AGENTS.md\n  - 工具技巧 → TOOLS.md\n  - 今日事件 → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n  - 用户偏好 → memory/about-user.md\n- 📤 **通知**：完成后发送总结到飞书\n\n**反思重点：**\n- ✅ 什么做得好？（保留成功经验）\n- ❌ 什么出了问题？（记录错误教训）\n- 💡 学到了什么？（具体可操作的洞察）\n\n明天凌晨2点就会第一次运行！这样我就能持续学习进步，更好地为主人服务了 🦞\n\n需要调整反思时间或内容吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774013471813}}
