{"type":"message","id":"8a34c61d","parentId":"4e23c6b9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T13:33:46.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我更新反思任务，在反思完成后自动备份到 GitHub："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"function.cron:57","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"d0aff8be-c82f-4fc5-aa1f-8e3a20f50a03","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行每日自我反思任务：\n\n1. 查看过去24小时内的会话记录（使用 sessions_list --activeMinutes 1440）\n2. 分析每个会话：\n   - 什么做得好？（任务顺利完成、高效工具使用等）\n   - 什么出了问题？（错误、重试、误解等）\n   - 学到了什么？（具体、可操作的教训）\n3. 将反思结果写入适当的文件：\n   - 流程改进 → AGENTS.md\n   - 工具使用技巧 → TOOLS.md  \n   - 今日事件 → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n   - 用户偏好 → memory/about-user.md\n4. 生成简短总结（2-4句话）\n\n5. 反思完成后，执行 GitHub 备份：\n   - 进入 workspace 目录\n   - git add .\n   - git commit -m \"每日反思更新: $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\"\n   - git push origin main\n\n注意：\n- 只提取真正的教训，不要简单总结\n- 检查是否已有类似记录，避免重复\n- 保持简洁具体，不要泛泛而谈\n- 确保备份包含所有更新后的文件"}}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774013586823}}
